0style%20looks%20like%20it%20belongs%20on%20a%20fishing%20boat.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20have%20a%20regular%20baseball%20hat%20from%20the%20brand%20that%20I%20wear%20for%20more%20active%20days%2C%20and%20a%20bucket%20hat%20that%20I%20wear%20at%20the%20pool%20or%20while%20gardening.%20These%20aren't%20the%20only%20styles%2C%20but%20they're%20the%20two%20most%20popular%20ones.%20Each%20comes%20in%20multiple%20colors%2C%20and%20the%20materials%20are%20extremely%20lightweight.%20Both%20styles%20are%20cute%2C%20comfy%2C%20and%20keep%20me%20from%20melting%20like%20a%20popsicle%20in%20the%20heat.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22f4fd1b98-814e-4c54-8c87-23674ede49f4%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20Mission%20cooling%20hats%20work%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Side-by-side%20collage.%20Left%20side%20illustrates%20a%20close%20up%20selfie%20of%20a%20person%20smiling%20as%20they%20appear%20wearing%20glasses%20and%20a%20white%20cap.%20Right%20side%20depicts%20two%20people%20posing%20as%20they%20smile%20for%20a%20selfie%20in%20the%20middle%20of%20an%20open%20landscape.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F62d70e2cbc4c770018b77721%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EMe%20wearing%20a%20Mission%20cooling%20hat%20on%20multiple%20hikes%20through%20Acadia%20National%20Park%20and%20in%20downtown%20Bar%20Harbor.%20%3Cp%3ESally%20Kaplan%2FInsider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EMission%20is%20pretty%20tight-lipped%20about%20the%20technology%20of%20their%20material%2C%20except%20to%20say%20that%20it%20%26quot%3Benhances%26quot%3B%20the%20process%20of%20evaporation%2C%20pulling%20heat%20away%20from%20the%20body%20and%20into%20the%20air.%20To%20activate%20the%20vaporactive%20cooling%20technology%2C%20the%20lightweight%20material%20has%20to%20be%20wet.%20The%20second%20you%20dampen%20it%2C%20you'll%20get%20an%20immediate%20cooling%20effect%20(you%20can%20do%20this%20with%20regular%20water%20or%20let%20your%20sweat%20do%20the%20work%20for%20you).%20But%2C%20unlike%20regular%20hats%2C%20the%20material%20remains%20cool%20to%20the%20touch%20instead%20of%20trapping%20steam%20and%20warming%20up%20as%20the%20sun%20beats%20down%20on%20you.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOnce%20the%20hat%20is%20wet%2C%20I've%20found%20that%20my%20sweat%20keeps%20it%20naturally%20damp%20and%20cool%20so%20I%20rarely%20(if%20ever)%20have%20to%20re-wet%20it%20on%20a%20long%20day%20out.%20But%20if%20you're%20just%20sitting%20by%20a%20pool%20or%20on%20a%20boat%20and%20you're%20not%20working%20up%20a%20sweat%2C%20you%20may%20want%20to%20re-wet%20the%20hat%20every%20hour%20or%20so.%20You%20can%20even%20hand-wash%20the%20hat%20with%20soap%20or%20detergent%20in%20between%20wears.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22bfcae167-e9fb-4f68-8470-8c9cfe7d6011%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3ETemperature%20test%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Side-by-side%20collage.%20Left%20and%20right%20side%20illustrate%20a%20person%20holding%20up%20a%20white%20cap%20as%20they%20test%20the%20temperature%20by%20pointing%20an%20orange%20temperature%20check%20gun%20towards%20the%20white%20hat%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F62d81a5bd99af30019c61d02%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EIt's%20a%20bit%20hard%20to%20see%2C%20but%20the%20thermometer%20reads%2077.7%20degrees%20on%20the%20left%20(dry%20hat)%20and%2054.5%20degrees%20on%20the%20right%20(wet%20hat).%20The%20test%20was%20done%20with%20room%20temperature%20water%20on%20a%2090-degree%20day.%3Cp%3ESally%20Kaplan%2FInsider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI%20did%20a%20little%20test%20outside%20on%20a%2090-degree%20day%20using%20a%20laser%20thermometer%20where%20I%20measured%20the%20temperature%20of%20the%20hat%20before%20and%20after%20dumping%20room-temperature%20water%20(about%2070%20degrees)%20on%20it.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20dry%20hat%20was%2077.7%20degrees%20and%2C%20after%20dumping%20water%20on%20it%2C%20the%20wet%20hat%20measured%2054.5%20degrees.%20For%20reference%2C%20I%20performed%20the%20same%20test%20with%20the%20same%20cup%20of%20water%20on%20a%20regular%20cotton%20hat%2C%20and%20it%20measured%20just%20over%2074%20degrees%20when%20wet%20%E2%80%94%2020%20degrees%20warmer%20than%20the%20wet%20Mission%20hat.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22d270b576-8ecb-4e74-8258-ecf43d3aabf5%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EComfort%20and%20fit%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20author%20in%20a%20Mission%20cooling%20bucket%20hat%20in%20a%20green%20and%20blue%20pattern.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F62d82ec50c98f500195eacf2%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222274%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EWearing%20a%20Mission%20cooling%20bucket%20hat%20at%20the%20pool.%20I%20like%20to%20dunk%20it%20in%20the%20water%20and%20keep%20it%20on%20while%20floating%20around%20to%20protect%20my%20head%20and%20neck.%3Cp%3ESally%20Kaplan%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20baseball%20hat%20fits%20well%20and%20has%20an%20adjustable%20band%20like%20any%20other%20athletic%20hat.%20I%20have%20a%20small%20head%2C%20and%20it's%20not%20too%20big%20for%20me.%20Same%20goes%20for%20the%20bucket%20hat%20%E2%80%94%20it's%20not%20too%20big%20around%20my%20head%2C%20but%20has%20an%20adjustable%20chin%20strap%20that%20can%20be%20tucked%20into%20the%20hat%20or%20tightened%20against%20the%20chin%20for%20a%20more%20secure%20fit.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Mission%20bucket%20hat%20is%20definitely%20a%20little%20goofier%2C%20but%20it's%20great%20for%20days%20on%20the%20water%20when%20I%20don't%20want%20my%20hat%20to%20blow%20away.%20The%20bucket%20hat%20is%20also%20UPF%2050%2C%20so%20I%20know%20I%20won't%20get%20burnt%20through%20it%20if%20I'm%20out%20on%20a%20boa