Others%20are%20more%20of%20a%20personal%20preference%2C%20such%20as%20my%20digital%20photo%20frame%20and%20air%20fryer.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20my%20husband%20and%20I%20decided%20to%20spend%20the%20year%20traveling%20around%20the%20US%2C%20we%20knew%20we%20had%20to%20be%20very%20specific%20about%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fthings-always-pack-suitcase-frequent-traveler%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ewhat%20we%20packed%3C%2Fa%3E%20into%20our%20Subaru%20Forester.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20a%20thorough%20elimination%20process%2C%20we%20created%20a%20list%20of%20items%20that%20fit%20neatly%20into%20our%20compact%20SUV%2C%20while%20still%20allowing%20us%20to%20see%20out%20of%20the%20back%20window.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20we%20drive%20from%20coast%20to%20coast%2C%20I've%20realized%20which%20items%20I'm%20most%20grateful%20to%20have%20brought.%20Here%20they%20are.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EOur%2027-gallon%20storage%20bins%20keep%20everything%20organized.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224941%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20Greenmade%20storage%20bin%20with%20a%20black%20bottom%20and%20a%20yellow%20lid.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6849cc303d5881a51c1b3a52%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223706%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Greenmade%20yellow-lid%20storage%20bins%20are%20stackable.%3Cp%3EEmily%20Pogue%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EFrom%20the%20start%2C%20we%20decided%20to%20keep%20all%20of%20our%20belongings%20in%20some%20kind%20of%20container.%20This%20has%20made%20packing%20and%20unpacking%20the%20car%20quicker%20and%20easier%2C%20since%20everything%20has%20a%20designated%20spot.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEach%20Greenmade%20yellow-lid%20storage%20bin%20has%20a%20specific%20purpose%20%E2%80%94%20clothes%2C%20kitchen%20supplies%2C%20workout%20and%20outdoor%20gear%2C%20and%20more.%20I%20also%20like%20that%20the%20bins%20stack%20easily%20and%20can%20be%20tucked%20away%20in%20our%20accommodations.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EMy%20digital%20photo%20frame%20brings%20a%20piece%20of%20home%20to%20every%20place%20we%20stay.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225078%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20digital%20photo%20frame%20on%20a%20counter%20displaying%20a%20wallpaper%20of%20floating%20rock%20formations.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6849ce1af748d8c055f38200%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223809%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EMy%20digital%20photo%20frame%20allows%20us%20to%20feel%20connected%20with%20family%20and%20friends.%3Cp%3EEmily%20Pogue%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI'm%20a%20big%20printed-photo%20person.%20Our%20last%20apartment%20had%20multiple%20gallery%20walls%20with%20candids%20of%20our%20loved%20ones.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20when%20you're%20staying%20in%20a%20new%20accommodation%20every%20month%2C%20you%20can't%20exactly%20nail%20photos%20up%20on%20the%20wall.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20get%20around%20this%2C%20my%20husband%20got%20me%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhome%2Faura-digital-picture-frame-review%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Edigital%20photo%20frame%3C%2Fa%3E.%20All%20we%20have%20to%20do%20is%20plug%20it%20in%2C%20and%20the%20faces%20of%20our%20friends%20and%20family%20are%20instantly%20in%20the%20room%20with%20us.%20It%20adds%20a%20personal%20touch%20to%20an%20otherwise%20minimal%20space.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EOur%20rechargeable%20jump%20starter%20has%20already%20saved%20us.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224284%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20rechargeable%20jump%20starter%20laying%20on%20a%20wooden%20floor%20with%20one%20black%20wire%20and%20one%20pink%20wire%20attached.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6849df21f748d8c055f38406%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223213%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20rechargeable%20jump%20starter%20is%20simple%20to%20use.%3Cp%3EEmily%20Pogue%3C%2Fp