%20healthy%20financial%20cushion%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20was%20ready%20to%20take%20a%20risk%20and%20create%20a%20new%20company.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20noticed%20a%20problem%20around%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-much-do-big-tech-companies-pay-their-employees-2022-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EBig%20Tech%20compensation%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20concentration%20risk.%20I%20saw%20an%20opportunity%20to%20help%20build%20a%20solution%20and%20educate%20employees%20on%20this%20risk.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEntrepreneurship%20has%20been%20a%20lot%20harder%20than%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbig-tech-not-right-fit-for-you-fit-into-categories-2025-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eworking%20in%20Big%20Tech%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20but%20I've%20found%20it%20far%20more%20fulfilling.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2227ae5322-fc45-47cd-9cf0-c840d6ceb699%5C%22%3EWhile%20working%20in%20Big%20Tech%2C%20I%20spotted%20a%20massive%20business%20opportunity%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EPrior%20to%20founding%20Cache%2C%20I%20spent%20most%20of%20my%20career%20focusing%20on%20data%20visualization.%20In%202014%2C%20Uber%20recruited%20me%20to%20lead%20a%20data%20visualization%20application%20suite.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20stayed%20at%20Uber%20for%20six%20years%20and%20eventually%20became%20a%20staff%20engineer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you%20work%20at%20a%20company%20like%20Uber%20for%20a%20long%20time%2C%20a%20lot%20of%20your%20compensation%20is%20in%20the%20form%20of%20stock%2C%20sometimes%20outsizing%20your%20cash%20compensation.%20As%20the%20company%20grows%20and%20does%20well%2C%20your%20net%20worth%20grows%20in%20line%20with%20the%20stock.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20creates%20wealth%20for%20the%20people%20who%20hold%20that%20stock%2C%20but%20having%20way%20too%20much%20of%20your%20net%20worth%20in%20a%20few%20stocks%20means%20you're%20taking%20undue%20risk.%20Take%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdeath-cross-formation-tesla-stock-price-bearish-signal-tariff-volatility-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ETesla%3C%2Fa%3E.%20In%20recent%20months%2C%20some%20people%20who%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.nl%2Fteslas-stock-slump-is-driving-wall-street-crazy-but-not-elon-musks-employees%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eworked%20at%20Tesla%3C%2Fa%3E%20may%20have%20seen%20their%20net%20worth%20fluctuate%20due%20to%20the%20changing%20value%20of%20the%20company's%20stock.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPeople%20tend%20to%20hold%20on%20to%20these%20massive%20stock%20positions%20due%20to%20inertia%20and%20because%20the%20taxes%20for%20reallocating%20stock%20can%20be%20very%20expensive.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20joined%20Uber%20at%20a%20good%20time.%20The%20company%20mostly%20did%20well%20and%20went%20public%20in%202019.%20All%20of%20the%20wealth%20I%20had%20accumulated%20in%20stock%20became%20real%20money%20on%20the%20open%20market%20that%20I%20could%20sell%20or%20trade.%20However%2C%20I%20had%20a%20lot%20of%20low-basis%20stocks%20that%20would%20trigger%20a%20high%20capital%20gains%20bill%20if%20I%20sold%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20joined%20Waymo%20in%202020%2C%20my%20Alphabet%20colleagues%20talked%20about%20similar%20problems.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20found%20this%20issue%20unsettling.%20A%20steep%20drop%20in%20stock%20price%20at%20the%20start%20of%20the%20COVID-19%20pandemic%20affected%20my%20portfolio.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20hired%20a%20wealth%20manager%20to%20help%20me%20find%20solutions%20for%20concentration%20risk.%20They%20showed%20me%20products%20that%20help%20people%20of%20high%20net%20worth%20manage%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstock-portfolio-unbalanced-index-growth-value-investing-blackrock-inflation-diversification-2024-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Econcentration%20risk%3C%2Fa%3E.%20One%20option%20is%20depositing%20concentrated%20stock%20into%20an%20exchange%20fund%20where%20others%20have%20done%20the%20same%2C%20and%20receiving%20fund%20uni