ding%20a%20company%3C%2Fa%3E%20myself%20involved%20a%20lot%20of%20learning%20on%20the%20job.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20wasn't%20really%20a%20manual%20I%20could%20follow%20for%20building%20an%20exchange%20fund%2C%20so%20we%20had%20to%20do%20a%20lot%20of%20R%26amp%3BD.%20There%20were%20many%20steps%20involved%2C%20including%20working%20with%20the%20SEC%20and%20FINRA%20to%20get%20the%20right%20registrations%2C%20since%20the%20industry%20is%20highly%20regulated%2C%20and%20building%20the%20technical%20infrastructure%20for%20a%20brokerage%20system.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20was%20one%20of%20the%20first%20users%20of%20my%20own%20product%2C%20and%20I%20invested%20a%20lot%20of%20my%20Uber%20stock%20in%20our%20exchange%20funds.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%226092359e-6706-4091-8c71-d3dae0fe8982%5C%22%3EI%20find%20entrepreneurship%20more%20fulfilling%20than%20Big%20Tech%2C%20but%20the%20journey%20is%20hard%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fentrepreneurship-guides-successful-startups-venture-capital-2019-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ERunning%20a%20startup%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20very%20different%20from%20working%20at%20a%20Big%20Tech%20company.%20I'm%20probably%20working%20triple%20the%20time%20I%20was%20before.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBeing%20employed%20in%20Big%20Tech%20was%20a%20very%20comfortable%20life.%20You%20worked%20on%20challenging%20problems%20and%20got%20paid%20well%20to%20do%20it.%20While%20I%20enjoyed%20this%2C%20I%20also%20wanted%20to%20figure%20out%20my%20own%20path.%20The%20entrepreneurial%20journey%20has%20been%20more%20fulfilling.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI've%20had%20to%20go%20through%20personal%20trials%2C%20such%20as%20not%20paying%20myself%20for%20the%20first%20year%20after%20leaving%20Waymo.%20Because%20of%20my%20financial%20cushion%20from%20working%20in%20Silicon%20Valley%2C%20the%20stress%20of%20this%20didn't%20really%20bear%20on%20me.%20I'd%20made%20sure%20I%20had%20several%20years%20of%20living%20expenses%20in%20reserve%20before%