v%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMy%20great-grandfather%20was%20quite%20a%20prominent%20person%20in%20his%20village%20of%20Yazd.%20One%20day%2C%20while%20on%20his%20way%20to%20work%20in%20his%20%3Cem%3Esavari%20%3C%2Fem%3E(the%20elite%20would%20ride%20donkeys%20back%20in%20the%20day)%2C%20he%20came%20across%20an%20inebriated%20Muslim%20beggar%20who%20demanded%20he%20get%20down%20from%20the%20donkey%20and%20show%20some%20respect%20to%20him.%E2%80%9D%20Ardeshir%20refused%20to.%20Thus%20followed%20an%20altercation%2C%20which%20ended%20with%20the%20beggar%20being%20hurt.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20hurting%20a%20Muslim%20was%20a%20grave%20offence.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMarzban%20contextualises%20this%2C%20referencing%20the%20religious%20persecutions%20that%20were%20rampant%20at%20the%20time.%20%E2%80%9CZorastrians%20had%20to%20practice%20their%20faith%20in%20hiding.%20To%20further%20humiliate%20them%2C%20a%20law%20had%20been%20passed%20that%2C%20whatever%20a%20person%E2%80%99s%20status%2C%20if%20they%20were%20on%20their%20way%20and%20should%20come%20upon%20a%20Muslim%2C%20they%20had%20to%20get%20off%20their%20%3Cem%3Esafari%20%3C%2Fem%3Eand%20tip%20their%20hat%20and%20do%20%3Cem%3Esalaam%20%3C%2Fem%3E(offer%20a%20greeting).%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%229669016977%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EArdeshir%20had%20clearly%20flouted%20the%20law.%20Fleeing%20seemed%20the%20only%20solution.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CSo%20he%20grabbed%20that%20era%E2%80%99s%20equivalent%20of%20Rs%208%20and%20fled%20by%20boat%20out%20of%20Yazd%20to%20a%20place%20called%20Quetta%2C%20where%20his%20aunt%20lived%2C%E2%80%9D%20Marzban%20goes%20on%20to%20detail%20how%20Ardeshir%20detested%20those%20months.%20He%20moved%20once%20more%2C%20this%20time%20with%20his%20sights%20trained%20on%20the%20docks%20of%20Bombay.%20But%20a%20few%20months%20of%20toil%20taught%20him%20this%20was%20not%20his%20cup%20of%20tea.%20He%20moved%20again.%20This%20time%2C%20he%20landed%20in%20Pune%2C%20spotted%20chaos%20unfurling%20at%20one%20of%20the%20bars%2C%20causing%20him%20to%20ideate%20an%20experiment%20that%20gave%20the%20city%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2Fweb-stories%2Fbanta-goli-soda-history-legacy-pallonji-soda-heritage%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ean%20indelible%20piece%20of%20fizzy%20history%3C%2Fa%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2Fardeshirs-1750416733.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Ardeshir's%20in%20Pune%20has%20some%20bestseller%20drinks%20like%20orangeade%2C%20lemonade%2C%20raspberry%20and%20ice%20cream%20soda%20and%20teekha%20(spicy)%20ginger%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2Fardeshirs-1750416733.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2Fardeshirs-1750416733-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2Fardeshirs-1750416733-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2Fardeshirs-1750416733-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2Fardeshirs-1750416733-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-452549%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EArdeshir%E2%80%99s%20in%20Pune%20has%20some%20bestseller%20drinks%20like%20orangeade%2C%20lemonade%2C%20raspberry%20and%20ice%20cream%20soda%20and%20%3Cem%3Eteekha%20%3C%2Fem%3E(spicy)%20ginger%2C%20Picture%20