2C%20if%20you%20will.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EA%20yellowing%20recipe%20and%20a%20hefty%20legacy%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStep%20into%20one%20of%20Pune%E2%80%99s%20Iranian%20eateries%2C%20and%20you%E2%80%99ll%20spot%20a%20familiar%20silhouette.%20The%20Ardeshir%E2%80%99s%20bottle%20is%20unmistakable.%20It%E2%80%99s%20also%20a%20weighty%20legacy%20to%20carry%20forward%2C%20Marzban%20learnt%20when%20entrusted%20with%20the%20business%20in%202013%2C%20following%20the%20passing%20of%20his%20father.%20%E2%80%9CI%20did%20not%20know%20anything%20at%20the%20time.%20How%20do%20I%20make%20the%20flavours%3F%20What%20do%20I%20do%3F%20And%20then%2C%20I%20came%20across%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F305528%2Fcookbook-baking-food-history-books-recommended-by-madhur-jaffrey%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ean%20old%20yellow%20notebook%3C%2Fa%3E%20where%20my%20father%20had%20scribbled%20down%20the%20formulas%20for%20the%20drink.%20I%20started%20going%20through%20his%20files%2C%20deciphering%20the%20scribbles%2C%20experimenting%2C%20tweaking%20and%20attempting%20to%20do%20justice%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20recalls.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENeither%20time%20nor%20the%20emergence%20of%20other%20drink%20alternatives%20has%20weathered%20Ardeshir%E2%80%99s%20popularity.%20Marzban%20learnt%20this%20one%20afternoon%2C%20when%20he%20was%20paid%20a%20visit%20by%20an%20elderly%20gentleman%20from%20the%20United%20States.%20%E2%80%9CHe%E2%80%99d%20been%20hunting%20long%20for%20the%20place%20%E2%80%94%20we%20don%E2%80%99t%20have%20a%20board%2C%20you%20see.%20Finally%2C%20someone%20told%20him%20where%20he%20could%20find%20the%20%3Cem%3Esodawala%20%3C%2Fem%3E(the%20man%20who%20makes%20sodas)%2C%E2%80%9D%20Marzban%20shares.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-instgrm-captioned%20data-instgrm-version%3D%5C%2214%5C%22%20data-instgrm-permalink%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel