hool%2C%20his%20friends%20would%20make%20fun%20of%20him%20for%20eating%20snails.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CSnail%20was%20considered%20a%20poor%20man%E2%80%99s%20food%2C%20or%20a%20farmer%E2%80%99s%20food.%20So%20we%20would%20hide%20it%20or%20not%20get%20it%20to%20school.%20Once%20we%20went%20to%20culinary%20school%2C%20we%20were%20taught%20about%20escargot%2C%20a%20french%20delicacy.%20I%20was%20pleasantly%20surprised.%20I%20remember%20thinking%2C%20%E2%80%98what%20is%20thought%20of%20as%20a%20poor%20person%E2%80%99s%20food%2C%20is%20a%20delicacy%20in%20France%E2%80%99%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Kumar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDebating%20over%20what%20to%20put%20on%20Semma%E2%80%99s%20menu%20led%20Roni%20and%20Chintan%20to%20add%20snails%2C%20which%20is%20a%20big%20hit.%20Chef%20Vijaya%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20%E2%80%98Nathai%20Pirattal%E2%80%99%2C%20which%20is%20the%20snail%20%3Cem%3Emasala%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20served%20with%20a%20%3Cem%3Ekal%20%3C%2Fem%3Edosa%20sells%20out%20on%20most%20nights.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERoni%20says%20Semma%20honours%20chef%20Kumar%20and%20his%20heritage.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20wanted%20to%20distinguish%20the%20restaurant%20by%20having%20a%20unique%20voice%20and%20perspective.%20Semma%20mimics%20the%20life%20of%20chef%20Vijay.%20It%20honours%20his%20heritage%20and%20includes%20integral%20moments%20of%20his%20life%E2%80%99s%20journey%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%2039-year-old%20Roni.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EFor%20Kumar%2C%20the%20menu%20is%20derived%20from%20his%20childhood%20memories.%20%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETake%2C%20for%20example%2C%20the%20Mulaikattiya%20Thaniyam%20(sprouted%20moong)%2C%20which%20his%20mother%20would%20make%20when%20he%20came%20home%20from%20school%20as%20a%20snack%2C%20or%20the%20Uzhavar%20Santhai%20Poriyal%2C%20which%20is%20made%20with%20vegetables%20bought%20from%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F293356%2Fhealth-benefits-of-kanj