is%20Vijay%E2%80%99s%20vulnerability.%20You%20truly%20get%20the%20chef%E2%80%99s%20perspective%20in%20his%20food.%20He%20has%20bared%20his%20soul.%20It%20is%20because%20he%20has%20owned%20who%20he%20is.%20And%20it%E2%80%99s%20liberating.%20We%20don%E2%80%99t%20have%20to%20fit%20into%20someone%20else%E2%80%99s%20rules%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Roni.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20love%20and%20feedback%20of%20people%20keep%20this%20team%20going.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COne%20day%2C%20I%20saw%20an%20old%20gentleman%20just%20sitting%20alone%20at%20the%20table.%20I%20asked%20him%20if%20everything%20was%20okay.%20He%20said%20that%20he%20was%20remembering%20his%20grandfather.%20The%20food%20he%20ate%20reminded%20him%20of%20eating%20at%20his%20grandfather%E2%80%99s%20house%2C%20and%20he%20said%20that%20since%20he%20left%20Chennai%20many%20years%20ago%2C%20he%20had%20never%20eaten%20anything%20like%20it.%20People%20have%20shed%20tears%20after%20eating%20the%20food%20as%20they%20remember%20moments%20from%20their%20childhood.%20They%20connect%20with%20us%20on%20a%20human%20level%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Roni.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhen%20you%20no%20longer%20bend%20to%20someone%20else%E2%80%99s%20rules%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20empowering%20to%20everyone%20around%20you%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Yoshita%20Rao%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20%3Cem%3EImages%20by%20Paul%20McDonough%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1750430161000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F10%2FCopy-of-Nathai-Pirattal-snails-photo-credit-Paul-McDonough-min-1665580840.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D452925%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Semma%E2%80%99s%20chef%20brings%20childhood%20memories%20and%20bold%20regional%20flavours%20to%20the%20global%20stage%2C%20earning%20one%20of%20the%20highest%20honours%20in%20the%20culinary%20world.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Sowmya%20Mani%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22c